data.description:
PRACTICALLY NEW AND JUST OFF The SHOWROOM FLOOR with ALL of the EXTRAS DONE for YOU! 
This POPULAR KIAWA FLOOR PLAN will keep your electric bills DOWN with SOLAR PANELS INSTALLED AND PAID FOR! This home ALSO includes a MAYTAG Water Softener System, Whole Home Air Treatment System by "Qualitair", Children's Playset, Garden Beds, Hunter Sprinkler System and Stained Privacy Fence. 
Need extra hot water? There are TWO Large Hot Water Heaters! 
This GEM has an Enormous Master Bedroom with private covered balcony with view, Separate Garden Tub and Shower, Double Sink Vanity with Modern Style Square Sinks, Toilet Closet with Storage Cabinet and a Walk in Closet that is the size of a Large Bedroom! Additionally, there are 4 Oversized Secondary Bedrooms (2 with huge walk-in closets) AND 3 FULL bathrooms. The Loft is a huge space for your family game or movie night and has ANOTHER walk-in closet, can we say STORAGE! There is an Office/Study downstairs with Double Glass Privacy Doors and 2nd Office Space built in Upstairs in the LOFT/ Second Living Room! Plenty of space for family and guests with Two Dining Rooms and an Eat in Island Breakfast Bar overlooking the Huge Living Room. The Spacious Kitchen features Double Ovens, Granite Counters, Island with Bar Stool Area, Stainless Steel Appliances, Drop in Electric Range, Premium Cabinets and Recessed Lighting. A Kitchen Walk-In Pantry with Ample Shelving conveniently leads to the Laundry Room and Garage with Electric Door Opener. Additionally, there are Two Big Covered Patios and TWO HVAC Units! You will not run out of space in this Beautiful Home in a Quiet Neighborhood, conveniently close to shopping, schools, restaurants, main highways and the military base but, far enough away from the hustle and bustle of the city. Make your viewing appointment before this Fabulous Home is SOLD!!!!
